   *    board   |             MCU                | Leonardo/Mega2560/M0 |    UNO    | ESP8266 | ESP32 |  microbit  |   m0  |
   *     VCC    |            3.3V/5V             |        VCC           |    VCC    |   VCC   |  VCC  |     X      |  vcc  |
