   *     RX     |              TX                |     Serial1 TX1      |     5     |   5/D6  |  D2   |     X      |  tx1  |
   *     TX     |              RX                |     Serial1 RX1      |     4     |   4/D7  |  D3   |     X      |  rx1  |
